#!/usr/bin/bash
FUNC=the-dash-dev-email-service
IMG=the-dash-dev-email-service:latest
REGION=us-east-1
REPO=176387286927.dkr.ecr.$REGION.amazonaws.com

docker tag $IMG $REPO/$IMG
docker push $REPO/$IMG

aws lambda update-function-code --region $REGION --function-name $FUNC --image-uri $REPO/$IMG
aws lambda update-function-code --region sa-east-1 --function-name my-function --image-uri $REPO/$IMG --output text > /dev/null
